    <li><strong>The Wake-Up Call:</strong> When a teacher apologizes for needing you, something is deeply wrong with the system.</li>
    <li><strong>A Different Question:</strong> Instead of "How do I handle all these crises?" I started asking "How do I prevent them in the first place?"</li>
